@jspark1105 We do not have measured int8 performance on Caffe2 yet but we do have measured int8 performance on IntelCaffe. You can check the following paper for details:
https://arxiv.org/abs/1805.08691
Please note that Broadwell does not support int8 inference. SKX or later processor families have the support.

